<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.2.4">
<l>piṟintēṉpeṟ ṟamakkaḷ peṇṭireṉṟivar piṉṉutavā</l>
<l>taṟintēṉnī paṇitta varuḷeṉṉumoḷ vāḷuruvi</l>
<l>yeṟintēṉaim pulaṉka ḷiṭartīrave ṟintuvantu</l>
<l>ceṟintēṉniṉ ṉaṭikkē tiruviṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I parted from [my] begotten children [and] wives,</l>
<l rend="indent">I who knew their further uselessness [to me].</l>
<l>I unsheathed and brandished the shining sword</l>
<l rend="indent">that is the grace you bestowed,</l>
<l>To end the suffering of [my] five senses. Coming in haste,</l>
<l>I clung to your feet, the one who dwells in Tiruviṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
